topic: 5.1.0 rvu on Win 64: Procedure entry point not found
body:
Just installed 5.1.0 on Win 7, and I get the following error message
with rvu now:


[ rvu.exe - Entry Point Not Found ]


The procedure entry point
?trimmed_helper at QString@@CA?AV1 at AEAV1@@Z could not be located in the
dynamic link library Qt5Core.dll.


Has anybody else come across this?


Thank you


Axel
